---
title: Cherry-and-Balsamic-Glazed Pork Chops with Crispy Broccoli and Potatoes
description: Part sweet, part tangy, and all-around delicious. That is what’s in store for you tonight with this thick and uber flavorful glaze. We keep the sides simple with roasted broccoli and potatoes to allow the pork to shine. And boy, does it steal the show.
